{"tid":1727101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推行動post］對家開始搵老解執垃圾打民意戰 我地搞返和理非活動！！！","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:30:42.000Z","uid":329698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"260cce792fa135a6cb9f2bafa9368972cf6bb1f3","tid":1727101,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割席<br />\n利申非分化撚 垃圾和理非一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話自己垃圾姐 唔係話緊我地全部和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑑於對家共匪開始玩民鬥民，佢地就係希望spin到淺藍中立群眾同我地對立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而開始減少暴力鎮壓，轉用「市民」收拾路障，甚至出動老解執垃圾，目的係讓藍屍更加憎恨我地，覺得老解都好過我地，甚至讓部分人轉藍。唔好忘記，藍屍真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有見及此，我地必須改變策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以讓佢地得逞<br />\n<br />\n繼續搞和理非遊行集會祈禱會，睇下對家反應，敵人反對先再升級，要讓港豬們見到我地唔係真&middot;暴徒，暴力升級只係自衛同讓正苦正視問題，而非<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無目的</span>使用暴力<br />\n<br />\n以上希望大家能參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩唔同意要屌9我<br />\n如果最後大家決定繼續暴力抗爭 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永遠都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nps 火魔前請三思 當下用火魔の意義 及 目的 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">萬萬不能</span>傷及無辜 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住我地唔係黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"37831e2d898b87dae2c9c337f2ffb43b2c707488","tid":1727101,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"bfb2f51512902225498c0feee876bf25b7752b24","tid":1727101,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"我知我係垃圾p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif